ru.yandex.subtitles.utils

Class IntArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.yandex.subtitles.utils.IntArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class IntArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    IntArrayList holds integers to Objects. It is intended to be more memory efficient than using an List<Integer> to store Integers objects, because it avoids auto-boxing.
